3Babsolutely%20say%20that%20he's%20right%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20she%20considers%20Palantir%20the%20Goldman%20Sachs%20of%20the%20tech%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20pulled%20people%20from%20Palantir%2C%26quot%3B%20Vyas%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20a%20home%20run%20every%20single%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVyas%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fheres-how-much-palantir-employees-make-salary-peter-thiel-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPalantir%20employees%3C%2Fa%3E%20tend%20to%20work%20long%20hours%2C%20and%20the%20company%20has%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20hands-on%20culture%26quot%3B%20that%20allows%20even%20junior%20employees%20to%20work%20alongside%20the%20firm's%20%26quot%3Bbrightest%20minds.%26quot%3B%20Having%20that%20proximity%20helps%20create%20a%20certain%20level%20of%20training%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVyas%20said%20another%20factor%20that%20makes%20Palantir%20stand%20out%20is%20its%20ability%20to%20recruit%20people%20who%20are%20passionate%20about%20their%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20something%20in%20the%20sauce%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Vyas%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20want%20to%20work%20on%20the%20complex%20problems%20because%20that's%20what%20excites%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJanelle%20Bieler%2C%20the%20head%20of%20US%20tech%20talent%20at%20global%20tech%20talent%20and%20engineering%20company%20Akkodis%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Palantir%20is%20known%20for%20hiring%20elite%20talent%20and%20candidates%20that%20tackle%20complex%20issues.%20While%20candidates%20still%20need%20to%20be%20individually%20evaluated%20on%20what%20they%20worked%20on%20at%20the%20company%2C%20she%20said%20working%20at%20Palantir%20signals%20%26quot%3Bintellectual%20horsepower.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20a%20recruiter%20sees%20it%20on%20a%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%2C%20it%20usually%20signals%20that%20this%20person%20went%20through%20a%20tough%20interview%20process%20and%20likely%20that%20they%20can%20hold%20their%20own%20in%20a%20pretty%20rigorous%20and%20fast-paced%20environment%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBieler%20added%20that%20Palantir's%20branding%20also%20stands%20out%20to%20recruiters.%20She%20said%20Palantir%20is%20neither%20regarded%20as%20Big%20Tech%20nor%20a%20typical%20startup%2C%20and%20the%20name%20has%20a%20level%20of%20mystique.%20Given%20the%20company's%20niche%20work%20environment%2C%20though%2C%20recruiters%20want%20to%20know%20that%20candidates%20can%20thrive%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20workplace%20settings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJason%20Saltzman%2C%20head%20of%20insights%20at%20CB%20Insights%2C%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider%20while%20working%20at%20a%20company%20that%20tracks%20employment%20changes%2C%20that%20%26quot%3BPalantir%20seems%20to%20be%20the%20stop%20on%20people's%20career%20journey%20that%20accelerates%20them%20the%20most.%26quot%3B%20Almost%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lennysnewsletter.com%2Fp%2F460d3466-f365-4799-9a70-352d8478e4c0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20quarter%20of%20former%20product%20managers%20at%20Palantir%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20since%20become%20founders%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEx-Palantir%20employees%20also%20tend%20to%20end%20up%20at%20a%20Big%20Tech%20company%20or%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20hottest%20startups%2C%26quot%3B%20Saltzman%20said.%20Google%20and%20Meta%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Anduril%20and%20OpenAI%2C%20employ%20many%20former%20Palantir%20workers%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20only%20is%20Palantir%20a%20rubber%20stamp%20on%20someone's%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20that%20allows%20them%20to%20go%20onto%20whatever%20they%20do%20next%2C%20but%20also%20many%20of%20them%20want%20to%20go%20solve%20the%20world's%20biggest%20problems%20that%20are%20shaping%20the%20future%20as%20we%20know%20it%2C%20either%20by%20joining%20a%20company%20or%20starting%20their%20own%2C%26quot%3B%20Saltzman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20Palantir%20stamp%20gives%20the%20founder%20credibility%2C%20which%20makes%20hiring%20early%20employees%20easier%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Alex%20Klein%2C%20founding%20partner%20at%20Nucleus%20Talent.%20Klein's%20company%20hires%20partner-level%20venture%20investors%20and%20early%20leadership%20for%20startups.%20He%20hasn't%20done%20any%20work%20for%20Palantir.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20founder%20or%20CEO%20who%20worked%20at%20Palantir%20for%20three%20years%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20they're%2027%20years%20old%20%E2%80%94%20will%20win%20the%20recruiting%20battle%20against%20the%2035-year-old%20founder%20who%20worked%20at%20a%20tier%20two%20tech%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20Klein%20added.%20%26quot%3BPalantir%20is%20absolutely%20a%20gold%20star%20on%20a%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226dafebfe-6253-47e5-86fb-0b9fa8d770c1%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESome%20say%20Karp%20could%20be%20overstating%20things%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAaron%20Sines%2C%20director%20of%20technical%20recruiting%20at%20global%20cloud%20consulting%20firm%20Edison%20%26amp%3B%20Black%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20while%20there's%20some%20truth%20to%20Karp's%20statement%2C%20overall%20he's%20seeing%20a%20%26quot%3Bresults%20revolution%26quot%3B%20among%20companies%2C%20where%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcollege-major-does-not-matter-former-google-employee2018-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoutcomes%20are%20placed%20above%20academic%20credentials%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20company%20names.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20team%20tells%20me%20all%20the%20time%20results%20are%20almost%20always%20coming%20over%20academic%20credentials%2C%26quot%3B%20Sines%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENatan%20Fisher%2C%20the%20cofounder%20and%20co-CEO%20of%20tech%20and%20legal%20recruiting%20firm%20SingleSprout%2C%20similarly%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bexecution%20matters%20more%20than%20brand%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bcompanies%20that%20want%20six%20plus%20days%20in%20the%20office%20are%20going%20to%20optimize%20for%20someone%20who%20is%20hungry%20and%20scrappy%20above%20all%20else.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20doubt%2C%20Palantir%20is%20a%20strong%20hiring%20signal%2C%20but%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20golden%20ticket%20in%20tech%20is%20outdated%2C%26quot%3B%20Fisher%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20real%20hiring%20market%20doesn't%20reward%20brand%20names%20alone%2C%20it%20rewards%20execution%20and%20adaptability%20%E2%80%94%20who%20built%20what%20and%20scaled%20systems%20at%20speed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20a%20gig%20at%20Palantir%20alone%20isn't%20necessarily%20a%20career%20maker%2C%20Fisher%20has%20seen%20an%20increase%20in%20tech%20companies%20hiring%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpalantirs-forward-deployed-engineer-role-churns-out-startup-founders-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EForward%20Deployed%20Engineers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20job%20title%20Palantir%20coined%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblog.palantir.com%2Fa-day-in-the-life-of-a-palantir-forward-deployed-software-engineer-45ef2de257b1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esoftware%20engineers%20who%20work%20directly%20with%20customers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFisher%20said%20that%20tech%20companies%20often%20seek%20to%20hire%20from%20%26quot%3Bmultiple%20high-caliber%26quot%3B%20talent%20pools%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-cards%2Framp-card%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERamp%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Stripe%2C%20Linear%2C%20and%20Notion%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20aren't%20clients%20of%20his.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESines%20said%20that%20Palantir%20has%20a%20reputation%20for%20seeking%20out%20top%20talent%20and%20having%20a%20%26quot%3Brigorous%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bresults-oriented%26quot%3B%20hiring%20strategy.%20However%2C%20he%20said%20that%20while%20it%20carries%20a%20%26quot%3Bbadge%20of%20honor%2C%26quot%3B%20for%20some%20clients%2C%20it%20may%20signal%20too%20much%20intensity%20for%20others.%20It%20depends%20on%20how%20companies%20perceive%20culture%2C%20Sines%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFarah%20Sharghi%2C%20a%20job%20search%20coach%20and%20former%20recruiter%20at%20tech%20companies%20including%20Google%2C%20Lyft%2C%20Uber%2C%20and%20TikTok%2C%20said%20that%20while%20Palantir's%20hiring%20process%20is%20%26quot%3Bvery%20stringent%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20good%20employee%20at%20Palantir%20may%20not%20be%20a%20good%20employee%20everywhere%20else%20because%20%26quot%3Bthere%20might%20be%20some%20nuances%20to%20some%20companies%20versus%20others%20in%20terms%20of%20cultural%20fit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20really%20subjective%20relative%20to%20what%20the%20company%20does%2C%20what%20their%20needs%20are%2C%20and%20so%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20culture%20may%20vary%20across%20tech%20companies%2C%20Sharghi%20says%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftips-find-tech-job-former-google-amazon-meta-recruiter-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20guiding%20philosophy%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20hiring%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20largely%20the%20same%20across%20the%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20not%20looking%20for%20breadth%20of%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20looking%20for%20technical%20depth%20of%20experience.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECalling%20Palantir%20the%20best%20credential%20in%20tech%2C%20as%20Karp%20did%2C%20%26quot%3Bflattens%20the%20reality%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTech%20is%20broad.%20What%20makes%20someone%20a%20great%20hire%20at%20Palantir%20doesn't%20always%20translate%20to%2C%20for%20example%2C%20a%20legacy%20company%20trying%20to%20modernize%20systems%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20takes%20a%20different%20skill%20set.%20There's%20no%20universal%20best%2C%20only%20fit%20for%20the%20problem%20at%20hand.%26quot%3B%3C%2F