ead%20to%20further%20mobile%20signups%20from%20customers%20looking%20to%20bundle%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAT%26amp%3BT%20beat%20expectations%20for%20its%20second%20quarter%20earnings%2C%20released%20in%20July%2C%20on%20the%20back%20of%20strong%20wireless%20and%20fiber%20subscriber%20growth%20and%20a%20multi-year%20estimated%20tax%20benefit%20of%20up%20to%20%248%20billion%20from%20the%20One%20Big%20Beautiful%20Bill%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20could%20face%20a%20more%20challenging%20second%20half%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20said%20that%20some%20of%20the%20second%20quarter's%20lift%20came%20from%20new%20customers%20pulling%20orders%20forward%20to%20avoid%20tariff-related%20price%20hikes%2C%20and%20that%20it%20was%20cautiously%20anticipating%20higher%20rates%20of%20customer%20churn%20in%20the%20latter%20half%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20assuming%20that%20we're%20going%20to%20continue%20to%20have%20a%20competitive%20environment%2C%26quot%3B%20AT%26amp%3BT%20CFO%20Pascal%20Desroches%20told%20analysts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERead%20more%20about%20John%20Stankey's%20memo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fatt-memo-john-stankey-lessons-corporate-culture-return-to-office-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E5%20things%20the%20AT%26amp%3BT%20CEO's%20sweeping%20memo%20says%20about%20where%20corporate%20America%20is%20headed%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fatt-ceo-john-stankey-email-employee-feedback-survey-rto-policy-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERead%20AT%26amp%3BT%20CEO's%20frank%20response%20to%20employee%20feedback%20about%20a%205-day%20RTO%20mandate%20%E2%80%94%20and%20much%20more%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-hardcore-era-employee-changes-att-memo-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECompanies%20are%20embracing%20a%20new%20hardcore%20culture.%20Here's%20what%20you%20should%20do.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20area%20that%20Stankey%20is%20reshaping%20is%20AT%26amp%3BT's%20workforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithout%20such%20a%20massive%20legacy%20copper%20network%20to%20support%2C%20most%20of%20AT%26amp%3BT's%20competitors%20have%20managed%20to%20grow%20with%20a%20comparatively%20smaller%20head%20count.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAT%26amp%3BT%20now%20has%20roughly%20141%2C000%20employees%2C%20and%20the%20company%20has%20taken%20several%20rounds%20of%20reductions%20in%20recent%20years%20to%20align%20its%20workforce%20more%20with%20its%20peers.%20Verizon%20has%2099%2C000%20and%20T-Mobile%20has%2070%2C000%2C%20and%20Verizon%20also%20gave%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fbusiness%2Ftelecom%2Fverizon-to-post-1-4-billion-severance-charge-after-4-800-workers-take-buyout-5cc96716%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuyouts%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year%20to%20some%204%2C800%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20increasingly%20strict%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fatt-5-days-office-return-mandate-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereturn-to-office%20mandate%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20AT%26amp%3BT%20has%20rolled%20out%20in%20phases%20over%20the%20past%20year%20has%20also%20resulted%20in%20further%20reductions%2C%20multiple%20employees%20have%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20and%20Stankey%20signaled%20in%20his%20memo%20that%20he's%20fine%20with%20more%20people%20leaving%20if%20they're%20not%20on%20board%20with%20the%20company's%20new%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20a%20self-directed%2C%20virtual%2C%20or%20hybrid%20work%20schedule%20is%20essential%20for%20you%20to%20manage%20your%20career%20aspirations%20and%20life%20challenges%2C%20you%20will%20have%20a%20difficult%20time%20aligning%20your%20priorities%20with%20those%20of%20the%20company%20and%20the%20culture%20we%20aim%20to%20establish%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20the%20memo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStankey%20has%20taken%20a%20similar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fatt-memo-john-stankey-lessons-corporate-culture-return-to-office-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emy-way-or-the-highway%3C%2Fa%3E%20approach%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20the%20company's%20chief%20operating%20officer%20who%20drove%20the%20acquisition%20of%20Warner%20Media%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2022%2F11%2F19%2Fbusiness%2Fmedia%2Fatt-time-warner-deal.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereportedly%3C%2Fa%3E%20led%20the%20division%20with%20a%20high-handedness%20that%20ruffled%20the%20entertainment%20executives.%20The%20move%20was%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20trend%20of%20network%20services%20providers%20seeking%20to%20own%20content%20producers%2C%20and%20Stankey%20(as%20CEO)%20shrugged%20off%20setbacks%20as%20he%20pursued%20a%20vision%20of%20expanding%20HBO%20to%20rival%20Netflix%20and%20Amazon%20Prime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAT%26amp%3BT%20jettisoned%20Warner%20Media%20in%202022%20at%20a%20loss%20of%20over%20%2440%20billion%2C%20and%20finalized%20its%20exit%20from%20the%20media%20business%20earlier%20this%20year%20when%20it%20sold%20its%20remaining%20stake%20in%20DirecTV%20to%20private%20equity%20firm%20TPG%20at%20a%20steep%20discount.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Stankey's%20apparent%20appetite%20for%20taking%20big%20bets%20seems%20unchanged%2C%20the%20circumstances%20around%20this%20chapter%20in%20the%20company's%20history%20are%20potentially%20more%20favorable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20sure%20there's%20a%20book%20to%20be%20written%20one%20day%20of%20how%20you%20can%20turn%20around%20your%20profile%20among%20investors%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20McHugh%2C%20the%20BNP%20Paribas%20telecom%20analyst%2C%20who%20said%20many%20long-term%20investors%20previously%20dismissed%20the%20company%20for%20its%20poor%20execution%20and%20misallocation%20of%20capital%20into%20non-core%20assets%2C%20like%20t