ng%20a%20signal.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOne%20lawyer%20said%20a16z's%20move%20could%20advance%20its%20founder-friendly%20reputation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAndreessen%20Horowitz%20wants%20startup%20founders%20to%20reconsider%20their%20relationship%20with%20Delaware%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20venture%20firm's%20own%20breakup%20with%20the%20state%20is%20more%20complicated%20than%20it%20seems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2022%2C%20the%20VC%20giant%20executed%20the%20plan%20it%20teased%20in%20a%20blog%20post%20earlier%20in%20the%20month%2C%20registering%20three%20new%20entities%20in%20Nevada%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F26040583-a16z-capital-management-llc-nevada-articles-of-domestication%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea16z%20Capital%20Management%20LLC%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F26040581-a16z-holdings-llc-nevada-articles-of-domestication%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea16z%20Holdings%20LLC%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F26040582-a16z-development-llc-nevada-articles-of-domestication%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea16z%20Development%20LLC%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20move%20wasn't%20just%20administrative%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20meant%20as%20a%20signal%2C%20part%20of%20the%20firm's%20effort%20to%20convince%20founders%20that%20Delaware%20shouldn't%20be%20the%20default%20choice%20for%20forming%20their%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAndreessen%20Horowitz%2C%20often%20called%20a16z%2C%20cited%20several%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fandreessen-horowitz-delaware-nevada-elon-musk-corporate-law-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereasons%20for%20moving%20to%20Nevada%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20stronger%20legal%20protection%20for%20corporate%20directors%2C%20tighter%20limits%20on%20shareholder%20lawsuits%2C%20and%20a%20business-friendly%20court%20system.%20It%20said%20this%20sets%20Nevada%20apart%20from%20Delaware%2C%20where%20an%20outsize%20share%20of%20America's%20business%20lawsuits%20are%20filed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20critics%20say%20a16z's%20beef%20with%20Delaware's%20corporate%20laws%20don't%20make%20much%20sense%20because%20it's%20not%20a%20corporation%3B%20all%20the%20entities%20that%20it%20moved%20to%20Nevada%20are%20LLCs%2C%20or%20limited%20liability%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20either%20being%20accidentally%20imprecise%20or%20intentionally%20disingenuous%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Samantha%20Prince%2C%20a%20law%20professor%20at%20Penn%20State%20University.%20%26quot%3BAndreessen%20is%20criticizing%20Delaware%20and%20its%20statutory%20corporate%20framework%2C%20but%20that%20doesn't%20apply%20to%20LLCs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2278d37f29-3e2e-4bc1-9c8b-3b9eaa805eb8%5C%22%3ENot%20all%20businesses%20are%20corporations%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELaypeople%20don't%20often%20draw%20distinctions%20between%20corporations%2C%20limited%20liability%20companies%2C%20partnerships%2C%20and%20other%20legal%20entities.%20Even%20lawyers%20and%20judges%20sometimes%20can't%20keep%20it%20straight%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpapers.ssrn.com%2Fsol3%2Fpapers.cfm%3Fabstract_id%3D4534991%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%202023%20paper%3C%2Fa%3E%20Prince%20co-authored%20found%20over%209%2C000%20references%20to%20%26quot%3Blimited%20liability%20corporations%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20don't%20exist%2C%20in%20court%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20differences%20matter.%20Corporations%20are%20bound%20by%20corporate%20law%20that%20sets%20baselines%20for%20what%20directors%20must%20do%20and%20the%20rights%20of%20shareholders.%20Delaware's%20corporate%20laws%20%E2%80%94%20and%20judges'%20decisions%20interpreting%20those%20laws%20%E2%80%94%20are%20what%20have%20some%20so%20angry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20contrast%2C%20limited%20liability%20companies%20are%20%26quot%3Blargely%20creatures%20of%20contract%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ben%20Edwards%2C%20a%20corporate%20law%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Nevada%2C%20Las%20Vegas%2C%20which%20means%20they%20generally%20write%20their%20own%20rules%20in%20their%20operating%20agreements%20and%20other%20agreements%20among%20their%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20states%20also%20have%20laws%20that%20outline%20how%20LLCs%20work%2C%20they%20can%20often%20be%20overridden%20by%20agreement%2C%20said%20Prince.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fed2459f-e644-43dd-a1ca-360ec3a86ad9%5C%22%3EFounders%20rule%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDelaware's%20body%20of%20corporate%20law%20has%20attracted%20big%20businesses%20for%20more%20than%20a%20century.%20Lawyers%20see%20the%20law%20as%20responsive%20and%20reliable%20because%20of%20the%20large%20number%20of%20cases%20interpreting%20it%2C%20and%20they%20generally%20praise%20the%20smarts%20and%20sophistication%20of%20the%20state's%20judges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20some%20have%20said%20Delaware%20court%20rulings%20could%20upset%20its%20business-friendly%20reputation.%20In%202024%2C%20two%20rulings%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-elon-musk-new-29-billion-pay-package-ceo-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Echallenged%20pro-CEO%20actions%20at%20Tesla%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Moelis%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%2C%20and%20another%20hit%20the%20brakes%20on%20Microsoft's%20acquisition%20of%20Activision%20Blizzard.%20Elon%20Musk%20responded%20by%20convincing%20investors%20to%20reincorporate%20Tesla%20in%20Texas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20blog%20post%2C%20Andreessen%20alluded%20to%20its%20interests%20in%20other%20companies.%20%26quot%3BFor%20founders%20considering%20a%20similar%20move%2C%20there%20is%20often%20a%20reluctance%20to%20leave%20Delaware%2C%20based%20in%20part%20on%20concerns%20for%20how%20investors%20will%20react%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20post%2C%20written%20by%20in-house%20lawyers%20Jai%20Ramaswamy%20and%20Andy%20Hill%20and%20government%20affairs%20partner%20Kevin%20McKinley.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20the%20largest%20VC%20firm%20in%20the%20country%2C%20we%20hope%20that%20our%20decision%20signals%20to%20our%20portfolio%20companies%2C%20as%20well%20as%20to%20prospective%20portfolio%20companies%2C%20that%20such%20concerns%20may%20be%20overblown%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20because%20Andreessen%20Horowitz%20isn't%20itself%20a%20corporation%2C%20it%20still%20needs%20to%20care%20about%20changes%20in%20corporate%20law%2C%20said%20Edwards%2C%20the%20UNLV%20professor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20%26quot%3Bmakes%20lots%20of%20investments%20in%20corporations%2C%20and%20so%20I%20think%20the%20criticisms%20that%20are%20saying%2C%20'They're%20not%20giving%20their%20real%20reasons%20because%20they're%20not%20a%20corporation%20themselves'%20are%20really%20misplaced%2C%26quot%3B%20Edwards%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20they%20have%20a%20strong%20and%20vibrant%20interest%20in%20the%20content%20of%20corporate%20law.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fa16z-dexit-nevada-llc-corporate-law-differences-2025-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1754422862000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689246d0f748d8c055f6ebb9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fa16z-dexit-nevada-llc-corporate-law-differences-2025-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Andreessen%20Horowitz%20moved%20its%20main%20business%20entities%20to%20Nevada%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20Delaware%20laws%20that%20a16z%20critiqued%20didn't%20really%20apply%20to%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jnewsham%40insider.com%20(Jack%20Newsham)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fa16z-dexit-nevada-llc-corporate-law-differences-2025-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Great%20Barrier%20Reef%20suffers%20worst%20coral%20dec