20Pentagon%20just%20inked%20a%20record%20%243.5%20billion%20deal%20with%20RTX%20for%20AIM-120%20air-to-air%20missiles.%20It's%20a%20massive%20order%20that%20underscores%20how%20global%20conflicts%20are%20stressing%20stockpiles%20and%20dramatically%20increasing%20demand%20for%20key%20munitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDemand%20for%20the%20AMRAAM%20has%20been%20growing%20amid%20global%20crises%20like%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20fights%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20massive%20deal%2C%20which%20was%20part%20of%20a%20total%20%247.8%20billion%20awarded%20to%20Lockheed%20Martin%20and%20RTX%20for%20missile%20production%2C%20was%20signed%20late%20last%20month.%20Other%20systems%20in%20the%20contracts%20include%20Lockheed%20Martin's%20Joint%20Air-to-Surface%20Standoff%20Missile%20(JASSM)%20and%20the%20Long-Range%20Anti-Ship%20Missile%20(LRASM).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AIM-120%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fair-force-jets-may-be-vulnerable-because-of-own-weapons-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAdvanced%20Medium-Range%20Air-to-Air%20Missile%2C%20or%20AMRAAM%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20award%20was%20especially%20notable%2C%20not%20only%20for%20its%20size%20but%20the%20number%20of%20allies%20and%20partners%20that%20will%20receive%20the%20missile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Foreign%20Military%20Sales%20portion%20of%20the%20massive%20contract%20includes%20Japan%2C%20Canada%2C%20Germany%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20and%20Ukraine%2C%20RTX%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20The%20Department%20of%20Defense%20contract%20details%20identified%20sales%20to%2019%20allies%20and%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20comes%20less%20than%20a%20year%20after%20a%20%241.2%20billion%20contract%20for%20the%20AMRAAM%2C%20another%20record-breaking%20deal%20that%20followed%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rtx.com%2Fnews%2Fnews-center%2F2023%2F06%2F20%2Fus-air-force-awards-rtx-1-15-billion-for-latest-amraam-configuration%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%241.15%2