20dependence%20on%20the%20aircraft%20for%20intercepts.%20There%20are%20multiple%20variants%20of%20the%20AIM-120.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20newest%20one%20is%20the%20AIM-120D%2C%20which%20has%20a%20reported%20range%20exceeding%20100%20miles.%20It's%20highly%20useful%20for%20taking%20out%20air%20threats%20like%20uncrewed%20aerial%20vehicles%20and%20drones%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20an%20expensive%20tradeoff%2C%20with%20each%20AIM-120%20costing%20around%20%241%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20has%20pursued%20alternatives%20to%20taking%20out%20these%20threats%2C%20and%20military%20officials%20have%20acknowledged%20that%20the%20need%20for%20more%20cost-effective%20answers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224138%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20F-16C%20Fighting%20Falcon%20assigned%20to%20the%2085th%20Test%20Evaluation%20Squadron%20shoots%20an%20AIM-120%20Advanced%20Medium-Range%20Air-to-Air%20Missile%2C%20or%20AMRAAM%20over%20testing%20ranges%20near%20Eglin%20Air%20Force%20Base%2C%20Fla.%2C%20March%2019%2C%202019.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6509d9e612dc4f001a168e61%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20F-16C%20Fighting%20Falcon%20assigned%20to%20the%2085th%20Test%20Evaluation%20Squadron%20shoots%20an%20AIM-120%20Advanced%20Medium-Range%20Air-to-Air%20Missile%2C%20or%20AMRAAM%20over%20testing%20ranges%20near%20Eglin%20Air%20Force%20Base%2C%20Fla.%2C%20March%2019%2C%202019.%3Cp%3EUS%20Air%20Force%20photo%20by%20Senior%20Airman%20Joshua%20Hoskins%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20the%20demand%20for%20the%20AIM-120%20is%20that%20it's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-fighter-scores-longest-aerial-kill-in-air-force-history-2021-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20highly%20desired%20system%20by%20militaries%20around%20the%20world%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20is%20an%20essential%20weapon%20as%20countries%20consider%20air%20dominance%20and%20defens