use%20House%20has%20been%20steering%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-plus-hulu-content-parent-controls-kid-accounts-pg-rating-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebundle%20subscribers%20to%20the%20Disney%2B%20app%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20loading%20it%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewith%20most%20Hulu%20movies%20and%20shows%C2%A0and%20some%20ESPN%20content.%C2%A0Unbundled%20Disney%20subscribers%20can%20also%20watch%20some%20Hulu%20and%20ESPN%20shows%20free%20of%20charge%20on%20Disney%2B.%20But%20Disney%2B%20content%20isn't%20available%20on%20Hulu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDisney%20CEO%20Bob%20Iger%20said%20in%20May%20that%20these%20changes%20are%20%26quot%3Bdefinitely%20having%20a%20positive%20impact%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20streamer's%20engagement%20and%20cancellation%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDisney%20is%20also%20making%20changes%20internally.%20It's%20discouraging%20Hulu-only%20ad%20buys%20and%20merging%20the%20platforms'%20ad%20servers%2C%20employees%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20sales-side%20employees%20said%20they%20need%20special%20permission%20to%20sell%20a%20Hulu-only%20ad%20spot%2C%20excluding%20certain%20interactive%20ads%20that%20only%20work%20on%20Hulu.%20They%20said%20the%20sales%20team%20is%20pushing%20advertisers%20instead%20to%20buy%20across%20both%20Disney%2B%20and%20Hulu%2C%20as%20part%20of%20what%20one%20of%20the%20staffers%20called%20a%20%26quot%3Bmassive%26quot%3B%20companywide%20push%20%26quot%3Bto%20prioritize%20Disney%2B%20over%20everything.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20last%20week%2C%20Disney%20moved%20to%20a%20unified%20ad%20server%20for%20Disney%2B%20and%20Hulu.%20This%20shift%2C%20known%20internally%20as%20%26quot%3BMission%20Control%2C%26quot%3B%20was%20labor-intensive%20and%20at%20times%20painful%20but%20necessary%2C%20the%20employees%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverything%20going%20through%20one%20ad%20server%20makes%20a%20lot%20less%20work%20for%20everyone%20involved%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20getting%20ad%20cam