Disney%2B%20and%20aren't%20necessarily%20interested%20in%20its%20family-friendly%20content%20dominated%20by%20franchises%20like%20Marvel%2C%20Star%20Wars%2C%20and%20Disney%20animation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20media%20analysts%20support%20Disney's%20direction%2C%20though%2C%20in%20going%20all%20in%20on%20Disney%2B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFurther%20integrating%20Hulu%20into%20Disney%2B%20could%20save%20the%20company%20about%20%243%20billion%20through%20%26quot%3Bthe%20elimination%20of%20duplicative%20technology%20and%20administrative%20costs%2C%26quot%3B%20MoffettNathanson's%20Robert%20Fishman%20said%20in%20a%20mid-July%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUBS%20media%20analyst%20John%20Hodulik%20told%20BI%20in%20July%20that%20Disney%20fully%20consolidating%20Hulu%20into%20Disney%2B%20is%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20steps%20they%20need%20to%20take%20to%20Netflix-ify%20their%20streaming%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDisney%20didn't%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220e6219f9-120c-4569-8215-d772f068f481%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EImpacts%20on%20Hulu's%20business%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Hulu%20still%20gets%20most%20of%20its%20viewership%20from%20its%20stand-alone%20app%2C%20there%20are%20signs%20Disney's%20emphasis%20on%20Disney%2B%20could%20be%20affecting%20its%20ad%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20analysts%20at%20MoffettNathanson%2C%20Hulu%20generated%20the%20most%20US%20ad%20revenue%20of%20any%20paid%20streaming%20service%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%2C%20thanks%20to%20its%20mature%20ads%20business%2C%20which%20launched%20in%202008.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Hulu's%20ad%20revenue%20fell%20an%20estimated%200.3%25%20last%20quarter%2C%20MoffettNathanson%20said.%20Hulu%20was%20the%20lone%20paid%20streaming%20service%20that%20didn't%20grow%20ad%20revenue%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%2C%20according%20to%20the%20firm.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Disney%2B%20saw%20its%20advertising%20revenue%20soar%2067%25%20year-over-year%20in%20that%20same%20span%2C%20MoffettNathanson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221856%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hulu%20ad%20revenue%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689216ed85e81483682f4b68%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22940%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMoffettNathanson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20that%2C%20Disney%2B%20has%20a%20long%20way%20to%20go%20to%20catch%20up.%20Hulu's%20ad%20revenue%20was%20more%20than%20four%20times%20that%20of%20Disney%2B%20last%20quarter%2C%20MoffettNathanson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHulu%20having%20slightly%20lower%20ad%20revenue%20year-over-year%20while%20Disney%2B%20has%20seen%20a%20huge%20increase%20makes%20perfect%20sense%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20first%20employee%20on%20the%20ad%20sales%20side%20said%2C%20considering%20the%20company's%20continued%20emphasis%20on%20Disney%2B%20over%20Hulu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20Disney%2B%20employee%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Beyeballs%20are%20shifting%20into%20the%20Disney%2B%20interface%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20line%20with%20what%20one%20of%20their%20Hulu-focused%20colleagues%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20Disney%2B%20and%20Hulu%20have%20seen%20gradual%20subscriber%20growth%2C%20even%20though%20Disney%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-streaming-profitable-price-hike-earnings-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehiked%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20each%20service's%20ad%20and%20ad-free%20tiers%20last%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHulu%20is%20well%20ahead%20of%20Disney%2B%20in%20how%20much%20money%20it%20makes%20per%20subscriber%20in%20the%20US.%20Hulu%20brought%20in%20%2412.36%20per%20subscriber%20in%20the%20first%20three%20months%20of%20this%20year%2C%20while%20Disney%2B%20only%20generated%20two-thirds%20of%20that%20sum.%20But%20Hulu's%20average%20revenue%20per%20subscriber%20has%20fallen%20in%20each%20of%20the%20last%20three%20quarters%2C%20while%20Disney%2