-Ganga-9_11zon-1730289587-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FAashraya-on-the-Ganga-9_11zon-1730289587-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FAashraya-on-the-Ganga-9_11zon-1730289587-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-373301%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20glorious%20view%20of%20the%20River%20Ganges%20along%20with%20surrounding%20fruit%20forests%20planted%20by%20Depi%20compensates%20for%20the%20long%20route%20to%20reach%20the%20homestay.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGetting%20here%20requires%20a%20beautiful%202.2%20km%2C%20one-hour%20moderate%20trek%20that%20takes%20you%20across%20a%20river%20bridge%20and%20then%20through%20a%20forest%20and%20a%20village.%20A%20good%20fitness%20level%20is%20required%20to%20walk%20this%20stretch%20comfortably.%20Our%20staff%20will%20receive%20you%20at%20the%20starting%20point%20of%20the%20trek%20and%20help%20you%20out%20with%20your%20luggage.%20Mules%20can%20be%20hired%20on%20prior%20request%20at%20Rs%20300%20per%20mule%20(to%20be%20paid%20by%20guests)%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20quickly%20adds%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F281316%2Frail-routes-train-journeys-scenic-beautiful-hills-valleys-india-vacation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20glorious%20views%3C%2Fa%3E%20compensate%20for%20this%20effort.%20Being%20so%20cut%20off%20from%20the%20city%2C%20Aashraya%20has%20adapted%20to%20meet%20its%20own%20needs.%20Creating%20this%20universe%20of%20self-sufficiency%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20easy%2C%20as%20Depi%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20been%20a%20slow%20and%20tedious%20process%20that%20has%20taken%20many%20years%20to%20build.%20For%20the%20first%20fifteen%20days%20of%20my%20stay%20here%2C%20I%20ate%20the%20same%20meal%20for%20breakfast%2C%20lunch%2C%20and%20dinner.%20There%20was%20no%20electricity%2C%20and%20I%20was%20living%20in%20a%20tent%2C%E2%80%9D%20his%20voice%20trails%20off%20as%20he%20reflects%20on%20those%20days.%20Many%20times%2C%20Depi%20felt%20alone%20in%20the%20journey%20to%20building%20this%20haven%20in%20Rishikesh.%20But%20even%20in%20those%20moments%20of%20solitude%2C%20nature%20kept%20him%20company%2C%20offering%20him%20help%20when%20he%20needed%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20know%2C%20soon%20after%20the%20three%20cottages%20were%20ready%2C%20a%20woodpecker%20began%20visiting%20us%2C%20pecking%20at%20the%20panes%20with%20impressive%20intensity.%20We%20would%20shoo%20it%20away%2C%20but%20it%20would%20return%2C%20moving%20from%20one%20cottage%20to%20the%20next.%E2%80%9D%20After%20several%20days%20of%20unsuccessfully%20trying%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20the%20bird%20%E2%80%94%20Depi%20laughs%20that%20they%20even%20kept%20a%20carpenter%20at%20hand%20to%20repair%20the%20damages%20caused%20%E2%80%94%20he%20realised%20the%20woodpecker%20was%20trying%20to%20convey%20a%20message.%20There%20were%20termites%20in%20the%20wood!%20After%20treating%20the%20wood%20with%20medication%2C%20one%20day%2C%20the%20woodpecker%20stopped%20visiting%20Aashraya.%20Its%20job%20was%20done.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FAashraya-on-the-Ganga-7-1730289678.jpg%3Ffit%3D1200%252C628%26quality%3D89%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20meals%20at%20Ashraya%20on%20the%20Ganga%20reflect%20local%20and%20indigenous%20culture%20and%20the%20produce%20for%20them%20is%20sourced%20from%20the%20neighbouring%20farms%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FAas