-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-30T235820.186-1754295642.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Archives%20of%20Umrao%20Jaan's%20cast%20featuring%20Rekha%20Ji%20(L)%20Dilip%20Kumar%20Ji%20attending%20a%20tournament%20organised%20by%20Taqi's%20late%20grandfather%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-30T235820.186-1754295642.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-30T235820.186-1754295642-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-30T235820.186-1754295642-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-30T235820.186-1754295642-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-30T235820.186-1754295642-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-480988%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPhotographs%20of%20Umrao%20Jaan%E2%80%99s%20cast%20featuring%20Rekha%20Ji%20(L)%20Dilip%20Kumar%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EJi%20attending%20a%20tournament%20organised%20by%20Taqi%E2%80%99s%20late%20grandfather%20(L)%20found%20in%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20archive%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20began%20my%20bachelor%E2%80%99s%20in%20mass%20communication%2C%20we%20were%20encouraged%20to%20explore%20the%20city%20with%20cameras%20and%20document%20what%20we%20saw.%20During%20those%20photo%20walks%2C%20I%20became%20fascinated%20by%20the%20people%20and%20the%20stories%20that%20lived%20within%20Lucknow%E2%80%99s%20streets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20content%20creation%20was%20never%20the%20first%20option.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20college%2C%20in%202014%2C%20I%20was%20shooting%20and%20making%20videos%20for%20various%20exhibitions%20and%20independent%20clients.%20I%20also%20worked%20on%20some%20write-ups%20for%20books%2C%E2%80%9D%20Taqi%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20waves%20of%20COVID-19%20gave%20many%20people%20time%20to%20pause%20and%20reflect.%20Within%20the%20four%20walls%20where%20others%20were%20exploring%20new%20ways%20to%20be%20productive%2C%20an%20idea%20was%20quietly%20brewing%20in%20Taqi%20Abbas%E2%80%99%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20states%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%202019%2C%20during%20the%20early%20wave%20of%20COVID-19%2C%20screen%20time%20increased%2C%20and%20I%20noticed%20a%20flood%20of%20content%20online%20about%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F314791%2Fmust-see-historic-monuments-structures-in-lucknow-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Lucknow%E2%80%99s%20culture%2C%20food%2C%20and%20heritage.%20%3C%2Fa%3EBut%20many%20of%20these%20stories%20lacked%20authenticity.%20Brand%20shoots%20weren%E2%80%99t%20happening%20either.%20After%20a%20lot%20of%20thought%2C%20I%20finally%20decided%20to%20start%20%3Cem%3ELucknow%20Uncovered%3C%2Fem%3E.%20But%20even%20then%2C%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20fully%20take%20shape%20until%20late%202023.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETaqi%E2%80%99s%20first%20step%20into%20content%20creation%20and%20what%20you%20can%20learn%20from%20it%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20all%20starts%20with%20humble%20beginnings%2C%20minimum%20gear%2C%20inspiration%2C%20and%20consistency%20for%20people%20in%20media%20production.%20His%20first%20video%2C%20shot%20with%20his%20friend%2C%20Arpit%20Massey%2C%20about%20the%20Hussainabad%20Picture%20Gallery%20in%20old%20Lucknow%2C%20reflects%20how%20a%20place%20was%20captured%20beautifully%20by%20making%20the%20most%20of%20the